column4: The people I work with have excellent knowledge of autism
column5: I feel that if a new person was to join the team and they disclosed they were autistic, they would be well supported and understood by others
column6: I feel that the management of the team are constantly improving their knowledge about autism
column7: It is easy to find information within the organisation about supporting autistic employees
column8: There are established pathways for autistic people to seek advice and support for managing their daily work activities
column9: The organisation has been proactive in making adjustments and providing autism awareness training for employees
column10: I think the organisation performs better than other organisations in the sector in terms of quality of support for autistic employees
